- **Pattern consistency**: Matches `StateManager` exactly — same assert guards, same WAL setup, same `_row_to_*` helper pattern

### Testing
- **19 tests covering**: model defaults, explicit fields, serialization roundtrip, DB creation, table existence, close idempotency, WAL mode, save/get roundtrip, not-found case, workflow_result JSON roundtrip (both None and non-None), list ordering, list limit, search on both columns, search no-match, search limit
